    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of updating and redecorating a building or other work, particularly with the implication of making it more energy efficient, eco-friendly, or sustainable. Used primarily in the context of built works.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
